## Implementation Priority Recommendation

Based on my assessment, if implementing these changes in order of impact:

1. **Must-have before Phase 2**: Changes 01, 02, 03 (schema versioning only), 06, 07, 08
2. **Should-have before Phase 7**: Changes 10, 12, 04 (timeouts only)
3. **Nice-to-have for polish**: Changes 09, 11, 04 (sharding), 05 (full visual system)
4. **Consider deferring**: JUnit XML (03 partial), quarantine expiry (05 partial)
